></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Gibt den <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a> oder <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/frameset\"><code>&lt;frameset&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Knoten des aktuellen Dokuments wieder, oder <code>null</code> falls keines dieser Elemente existiert.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>var objRef</em> = document.body;\ndocument.body = <em>objRef;</em></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// in HTML: &lt;body id=\"oldBodyElement\"&gt;&lt;/body&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"oldBodyElement\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> aNewBodyElement <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"body\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\naNewBodyElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"newBodyElement\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ndocument<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> aNewBodyElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>body<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"newBodyElement\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Anmerkungen","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>document.body</code>&nbsp;ist das Element, welches&nbsp;den Inhalt eines Dokuments enthält. In Dokumenten mit <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> Inhalt, gibt das <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> Element den Inhalt aus, in Frameset Dokumenten wiederum, wird das äußerste&nbsp;<code>&lt;frameset&gt;</code> Element ausgegeben.</p>\n\n<p>Da&nbsp;<code>body</code> setzbar ist, wird das Setzen eines neuen Body Elements alle aktuellen Elemente des existierenden <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> Elements entfernen.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"spectable standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/dom.html#dom-document-body\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Document.body' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/dom.html#dom-document-body\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Document.body' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/dom.html#dom-document-body\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Document.body' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-HTML/html.html#ID-56360201\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 HTML Specification<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Document.body' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Veraltet</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-html.html#attribute-body\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 1 Specification<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Document.body' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Veraltet</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_kompatibilität","title":"Browser Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>1</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>2</td>\n   <td>6</td>\n   <td>9.6 (möglicherweise früher)</td>\n   <td>4 (möglicherweise früher)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"warning notecard\" id=\"sect5\">\n<ol>\n <li>\n  <p>Obwohl <code>document.body</code> eine sehr gute Methode ist, um das <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> Element in HTML anzusprechen, wird es von Firefox nicht unterstützt, wenn der <code>Content-Type</code> nicht <code>text/html</code> oder <code>application/xhtml+xml</code> ist. Eine sicherere Methode um das <code>&lt;body&gt;</code> Element anzusprechen ist es,&nbsp;<code>document.getElementsByTagName(\"body\")</code> zu verwenden, welches einen Array mit einem einzigen Item ausgibt. Das ist übertragbar auf HTML und XHTML. Bei denen ist der <code>Content-Type</code> nicht im HTTP response header angegeben.</p>\n </li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td>5 (probably earlier)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/head\"><code>document.head</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"example"},{"text":"Anmerkungen","id":"notes"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"specification"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Gibt den <body> oder <frameset> (en-US) Knoten des aktuellen Dokuments wieder, oder null falls keines dieser Elemente existiert.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.body","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"document.body","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"document.body","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.body","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Document.body","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"document.body","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Document.body","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Document.body","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"document.body","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Document.body","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/document/body","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/document/body/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"Document"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/body","title":"Document.body"}],"pageTitle":"Document.body - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}